<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:300px;"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-5733/SuburbSlasher.jpg" style="width:300px;" class="enlarge" alt="SuburbSlasher.jpg" />
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:300px;">
